Dennisi!

271
00:33:33,250 --> 00:33:35,500
Pojď sem!

272
00:33:35,542 --> 00:33:36,751
Hned!

273
00:33:40,667 --> 00:33:42,125
Jsi skutečnej?

274
00:34:16,125 --> 00:34:17,167
Ne!

275
00:34:31,125 --> 00:34:33,026
Ne! Ne!

276
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:15,150
